nts Premium'=>'BuddyClients Premium','BuddyPress is missing.'=>'缺少 BuddyPress。','By creating an account, you agree to the %s.'=>'创建帐户即表示您同意 %s。','By default, the user will search help docs and have the option to contact.'=>'默认情况下，用户将搜索帮助文档并选择联系。','Can clients select multiple options for this field?'=>'客户能否为该字段选择多个选项？','Cancel'=>'取消','Canceled'=>'已取消','Cancellation reason...'=>'取消原因...','Cancellation Request'=>'取消申请','Cancellation Request Admin Notification'=>'取消申请 管理通知','Cancellation Requested'=>'申请取消','Cancellation requested.'=>'要求取消。','Cancellation Window'=>'取消窗口','Change setting.'=>'更改设置。','Change the text and link for the signup button.'=>'更改注册按钮的文字和链接。','Cheatin&#8217; huh?'=>'作弊？','Check for Payments'=>'付款支票','Checkbox'=>'复选框','Checkboxes'=>'复选框','Checking for New Payments...'=>'检查新付款...','Checkout'=>'结账','Choose from checkbox and dropdown Xprofile fields. <a href="%s">Create a new field.</a>'=>'从复选框和下拉 Xprofile 字段中选择。<a href="%s">创建新字段。','Choose or create your '=>'选择或创建您的','Clear Signature'=>'清晰签名','Click to %s.'=>'点击 %s。','Clicks'=>'点击次数','Client'=>'客户','Client Email'=>'客户电子邮件','Client Fee'=>'客户费用','Client Rate'=>'客户费率','Client Types'=>'客户类型','Closed'=>'关闭','Commission'=>'委员会','Commission Payments'=>'佣金支付','Commission Type'=>'委员会类型','Complete'=>'完整','complete'=>'完整','Complete Checkout'=>'完成结账','Complete the briefs for '=>'完成以下简介','Complete the new %s agreement by %s.'=>'在 %s 前完成新的 %s 协议。','Complete your <a href="%s">new affiliate agreement</a> by %s.'=>'在 %s 之前完成<a href="%s">新联盟协议</a>。','Complete your <a href="%s">new team member agreement</a> by %s.'=>'在 %s 之前完成<a href="%s">新团队成员协议</a>。','Complete your <a href="%s">team member agreement</a>.'=>'完成<a href="%s">团队成员协议</a>。','Completed'=>'已完成','Completed Bookings'=>'已完成预订','Components'=>'组件','Confirm Your Booking'=>'确认预订','Confirmation does not match. Files not deleted.'=>'确认不匹配。文件未删除。','Connect your Stripe account to BuddyClients in order to accept payments.<p>Once you have added the information, click "Validate Stripe" to test your keys.</p><p>It is recommended to first enable Test Mode to check that your Stripe integration is working properly.</p><p>The webhooks setup allows Stripe to "talk" to your website and notify you of a successful payment. If webhooks are not properly set up, your bookings will not change to "succeeded" when payments are successful.</p><p>If payments have been processed without webhooks set up correctly, use the "Check for Payments" button to repair bookings.</p>'=>'<p>添加信息后，点击 "验证 Stripe"，测试您的密钥。</p><p>建议首先启用测试模式，检查您的 Stripe 集成是否正常。</p><p>网络钩子设置允许 Stripe 与您的网站 "对话"，并在付款成功后通知您。</p><p>如果未正确设置网络钩子，则在付款成功时，您的预订将不会更改为 "成功"。</p><p>如果在未正确设置网络钩子的情况下处理了付款，请使用 "检查付款 "按钮修复预订。','Contact'=>'联系方式','Contact %s'=>'联系人 %s','contact %s'=>'联系 %s','Contact Form Admin Notification'=>'联系表单管理通知','Contact Form Only'=>'仅限联系表格','Contact Form User Confirmation'=>'联系表单用户确认','contact us'=>'联系我们','Content'=>'内容','Conversion Rate'=>'转换率','Conversion Rate:'=>'转换率：','Copy this link to your the Endpoint URL field for your Stripe webhook.'=>'将此链接复制到 Stripe 网络钩子的端点 URL 字段。','Count'=>'计数','Create a New Project'=>'创建新项目','Create adjustment fields for the most flexibility in your services\' customization and pricing.<p>When a user selects a service on the booking form, the attached adjustment fields will become visible.</p><p>Adjustment fields are excellent for add-ons, customization, and additional details that impact service pricing.</p><p>You can automatically add, subtract, or multiply the service fee based on the selected adjustment.</p>'=>'<br>当用户在预订表单上选择一项服务时，附加的调整字段将会显示出来。<br>调整字段非常适合附加项目、定制和影响服务定价的其他细节。<br>您可以根据所选的调整值自动增加、减少或乘以服务费。','Create booking and notify %s'=>'创建预订并通知 %s','Create brief types here. When creating services, select the applicable brief type(s). A brief of each type will automatically be generated when the service is booked.<p>For example, you could create a brief type called "Editing" and connect it to "Copyediting" and "Proofreading" services.</p>'=>'在此创建摘要类型。创建服务时，请选择适用的简介类型。<p> 例如，您可以创建一个名为 "编辑 "的摘要类型，并将其与 "校对 "和 "复制 "服务连接起来。','Create custom quotes for one-off projects.'=>'为一次性项目创建自定义报价。','Create fields for each brief type. For each field, specify how the field should be displayed on the brief form, including the field type, file upload settings, and checkbox or dropdown options, as applicable.'=>'为每种摘要类型创建字段。为每个字段指定字段在摘要表单上的显示方式，包括字段类型、文件上传设置以及复选框或下拉选项（如适用）。','Create file upload types to require different types of files based on the service(s) selected.'=>'创建文件上传类型，根据所选服务要求不同类型的文件。','Create New %s'=>'创建新 %s','Create Page'=>'创建页面','Create password'=>'创建密码','Create services.'=>'创建服务。','Create your services to get started. Only valid services will appear on the booking form.'=>'开始创建您的服务。只有有效的服务才会出现在预订表上。','Current Legal Agreements'=>'现行法律协议','Current License: %s'=>'当前许可证： %s','Current Page'=>'当前页','Custom Quote'=>'自定义报价','Custom Quotes'=>'自定义报价','Customize the BuddyClients plugin emails using these templates. Dynamic values are enclosed in double brackets, e.g. {{site_name}}.<p>To restore default email templates, delete the templates you wish to restore and click "Repair Email Templates."</p>'=>'使用这些模板自定义 BuddyClients 插件的电子邮件。动态值用双括号括起来，例如：{{site_name}}。<br>要恢复默认电子邮件模板，请删除要恢复的模板，然后点击 "修复电子邮件模板"。','Dashboard'=>'仪表板','Date'=>'日期','Date Created'=>'创建日期','Date Range '=>'日期范围','Date Registered'=>'注册日期','deactivate'=>'停用','Deadline'=>'截止日期','Default Client Type'=>'默认客户类型','Define the payment methods and commission percentage for affiliates.'=>'定义联属会员的付款方式和佣金比例。','Define the post type(s) of your help documentation, and specify the popup\'s display rules and content.<p>Options for popup content include a help docs live search and a contact form.</p><p>If both are selected, the user will first see the search. If their search returns no results, they will have the option to complete the contact form.</p>'=>'定义帮助文档的发布类型，并指定弹出窗口的显示规则和内容。<br>弹出窗口内容的选项包括帮助文档实时搜索和联系表单。<br>如果同时选择了这两个选项，用户将首先看到搜索。如果搜索没有结果，用户可以选择填写联系表单。','Define you